title: RHOC: Rocked to the Core Friends - Live from Austin!
description:
The Real Housewives of Orange County closes its 16th season out with a bizarre but catchy musical number that we shamelessly LOVE. But before then, there's a brush with Tommyknockers, a fight in a store, and a very confessional moment with a sommelier.

Thanks to the Moontower Comedy Festival for having us!
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
